  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbf - \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attempts by the President to leave the country failed - the US embassy also refused to issue a visa",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "India has denied Sri Lanka's request for AN32 aircraft to land at an Indian airport with the President",
        "Efforts by the President of Sri Lanka and 15 people, including his family and friends, to leave the country have failed due to procedural issues, top Air Force sources told SBS Sinhala Service.",
        "After leaving the Presidential Palace on the 9th and taking shelter at the Trincomalee Naval Base, he flew from Trincomalee to Rathmalana Airport on Monday in two Bell 412 helicopters.",
        "He went to Katunayake Air Force Base yesterday evening after holding talks with the tri-service commanders.",
        "A representative of the country's air force confirmed that Rajapaksa and his entourage were scheduled to fly to Dubai on Sri Lanka Airlines flight UL 225.",
        "But the immigration officials confirmed that Rajapaksa and his entourage arrived at Bandaranaike Airport's Immigration and Emigration Section to confirm their documents.",
        "Security forces prevented the President and his entourage from entering the public area, police and airport security personnel told the media.",
        "The SBS Sinhala Service has received information that the officials of the Department of Immigration and Emigration have refused to work in the areas for the most important personalities since the 9th.",
        "After that, the President and his entourage tried to board Etihad Flight 267 at the airport, but missed it due to technical reasons, airport sources said.",
        "Our media has received information that India has refused the request of Sri Lanka's AN32 aircraft to land at an Indian airport with the President.",
        "A security source confirmed that the President, who was staying overnight at the Katunayake Air Force base, was investigating how to get out safely.",
        "Gotabaya Rajapaksa, who renounced his US citizenship to run in the 2019 elections, requested a visa from the US embassy last week to travel to California, but the request was denied, diplomatic sources said.",
        "Diplomatic sources told SBS Sinhala Service that the Embassy reminded the President that a guest visa cannot be issued to a person who has renounced citizenship except in the most compelling circumstances.",
        "It was clarified that he could not be granted a visa. We reminded him that he can travel visa-free as head of state but the current circumstances are different, said a diplomatic representative.",
        "However, the US Embassy helped the President's younger brother in getting a new passport."
      ],
